title: Independent Candidate Usama Hamza wins NA-105 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): An Independent Candidate Usama Hamza has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-105, Toba Tek Singh I by securing 138,194 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz Candidate Chaudhry Kahlid Javed, who bagged 107,840, votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 56.60, percent.
